                                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">• Regular maintenance visits</li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">• Water chemistry balancing</li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">• Filter cleaning & replacement</li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">• System performance checks</li>
